{"tid":2025562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列違反國際法非法吞併西岸領土 巴勒斯坦宣布停止與美國、以色列包括安全合作在內所有協議","createTime":"2020-05-20T10:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T16:31:39.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"496f3061309cb4f37e5af45060db93016ad6c219","tid":2025562,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3171104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3171104&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=47a2bd7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3171104&h=16a80cae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3171104</a><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕由於領土爭議，巴勒斯坦領導人阿巴斯（Mahmoud Abbas）宣布，停止與以色列、美國的所有協議。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，阿巴斯所謂終止所有協議與義務，包括安全合作，此舉是回應以色列併吞巴勒斯坦領土的計畫，阿巴斯說，由於侵占巴勒斯坦領土，以色列必須承擔起所有的責任與義務，但阿巴斯並未敘述終止協議實務上會如何執行。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院先前傳出，準備承認以色列併吞約旦河西岸計畫，併吞區域為猶太人屯墾區。"},{"pid":"b92e35981451ed418f9f4e8ff59f8501245da90d","tid":2025562,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"six day war<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121ce43762a994a97da7ac7da314ee99e62d894e","tid":2025562,"uid":317378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"以色列明係pk黎，佢其實都冇得揀"},{"pid":"3be01ec69513ee849cad97a632714d90b3b615dc","tid":2025562,"uid":331421,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"唔夠人打唯有強調法律正統，<br />\n所有流亡政府都係咁"},{"pid":"2ae5581ba49d8dee8172cff8b4e6df82f823050d","tid":2025562,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:22:01.000Z","msg":"中國好似承認巴勒斯坦？"},{"pid":"3d6c874e4d51682a9d6772658b59a76f559af1df","tid":2025562,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike"